<div id='imageData' data-json='{"infobox":{"file":"3760053-logo.png","path":"10\/103881\/","mime":"image\/png","sizes":"scale_super,scale_medium,square_medium,square_small,scale_small,square_tiny,square_avatar,screen_kubrick,scale_large,scale_avatar,square_mini,screen_medium","caption":null},"background":[]}' />
==Overview== Sandman Team is a small independent video game development studio located in Ukraine. The first game released by Sandman Team was Through the Nightmares. The game is a side-scrolling platforming game that took the studio nine years to develop.
